Bring String
Bring List
Bring Json
Bring Time

Keep Greeting Prefix be "Hello"

Record Person
  Has Name as String
  Has Age as Int

  Teach Label using Self
    "{Name of Self} is {Age of Self}"

Teach Add using Left and Right
  Left plus Right

Teach Make Greeter using Prefix
  Teach using Name give "{Prefix}, {Name}"

Make Number be 3
Make Total be Use Add with Number and 4
Say "Total is {Total}"

Make Names be List with "Ada" and "Grace" and "Linus"
Make Loud Names be Use List Map with Names and Teach using Name give Use String Upper with Name
Say Loud Names

Make Long Names be Use List Filter with Names and Teach using Name give Length of Name is greater than 3
Say Long Names

Make Scores be Map with "Ada" meaning 10 and "Grace" meaning 12
Say Scores

Make Person be New Person with Name be "Ada" and Age be 37
Say Use Label of Person

Make Greet be Use Make Greeter with Greeting Prefix
Say Use Greet with "world"

If Total is at least 7
  Say "math works"
Otherwise
  Say "math is confused"

Repeat for Index and Name in Indexed Names
  Say "{Index}: {Name}"

Repeat for Step in Range from 1 to 3
  Say "step {Step}"

Make Maybe Name be Item 0 of Names as Maybe String
Match Maybe Name
  When Some First Name
    Say "first is {First Name}"
  When nothing
    Say "no names"

Match Use Int Parse with "271"
  When Success Parsed
    Say "parsed {Parsed}"
  When Failure Error
    Say Error

Make Json Text be Need Use Json Serialize with Scores
Say Json Text

Make Today be Use Time Format with Use Time Now and "yyyy-mm-dd"
Say "today is {Today}"
